@startuml
autonumber
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
actor "Utente" as User

box "Frontend (Client)" #LightBlue
    participant "VerifyForm" as UI
end box

box "Backend (Server)" #LightYellow
    participant "/api/verify" as API
end box

box "Database" #LightGreen
    database "PostgresDB" as DB
end box

activate UI
User -> UI: Inserisce Codice a 6 cifre

UI -> API: verify2FA(email, code)
activate API

API -> DB: getToken(email)
activate DB
DB --> API: Record Object (Con hash)
deactivate DB

alt Codice Errato
    API -> API: bcrypt.compare(token, hash) -> False

    API --> UI: 400 Bad Request (Invalid Code)
    UI --> User: Mostra "Codice non valido"

else Codice Corretto e non Scaduto

    API -> API: bcrypt.compare(token, hash) -> True
    API -> API: checkScadenza(token) -> True

    API -> API: Aggiorna JWT Session\n{ pending2FA: false }
    API --> UI: 200 OK (Verified)
    UI -> User: Redirect a /home

end
@enduml